      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, i might have mixed up major and minor in my head. so if i'm looking at the circle and moving clockwise vs counter-clockwise, how does that work with the key signatures? like, does the number of sharps or flats change in a specific pattern as i go around the circle?",
